.SUBCKT FUSE 1 4
*Connections Fuse+ Fuse-
*Optional Fuse temperature can be examined by bringing out
*node 59
* For 8AG Fuses Use 
* RCOLDE=-.3, HCTE=2.0, KS=5.3U, and TB=.5
